title: Cat Collar Personalised with Name Tag and Phone Number Engraved for Kitten Puppy (Velvet Rose Gold)
features: If you're looking for a non-breakaway, and worry your kitten easily take off their quick release collars, this cute cat collar will be a great choice
It's soft velvet touch cat collar, lightweight, easy to put on, safe for your fur baby
With the customizable feature of the collar, you don't have to buy a tag separately, costing you more money, The engraved lettering is small, but readable
Sturdy metal buckle with rose gold/ gold/ silver plating is more beautiful and durable than plastic clasps
The collars are easy to adjust, it also has a cute little bell that you can remove if you wish. Would recommend for indoor cats or small dogs
description: If you worried about your cats getting lost, it was time to buy a cute collar. These are not quick-release collars. Really top quality made, the velvet is very soft yet durable. You can remove that jingling bell if your cat was annoyed of it. Your kitten's name and phone number can be engraved on the metal buckle of the collar clearly and easy to read. Note that the more characters your input, the smaller the engraved letterings. Before order, please use a soft measuring tape or ribbon, accurate measure around the cat's neck to get a correct size. Adjustable Collar Perfect for all cats, small dogs puppy, such as Chihuahua, Yorshire, etc.
